('01dafd2b-fe05-4df0-ad4e-0012b06a8657', '08092025013', 'draft', '<h2><strong>1st Day : Ayodhya Arrival &amp; Local Sightseeing .&nbsp;</strong></h2><p>Ram Janmabhoomi</p><p>Hanuman Garhi temple<strong>,&nbsp;</strong></p><p><br></p><h2><strong>2nd Day : Ayodhya Local Sightseeing</strong></h2><p>Kanak Bhavan</p><p>Sita Mata Rasoi, Guptar Ghat, Treata ke Thakur</p><p>Chappiya</p><p><br></p><h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">3</strong><sup style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"><strong>rd</strong></sup><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"> Day :-&nbsp;Ayodhya to Varanasi Sightseeing&nbsp;</strong></h2><p>Arrival at Varanasi and transfer to the hotel</p><p>Ganga Aarti</p><p>Boat ride</p><p><br></p><h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">4</strong><sup style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"><strong>th</strong></sup><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"> Day - Varanasi&nbsp;Local Sightseeing.</strong></h2><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Kashi Vishwanath Temple,</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"> Annapurna Temple,</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"> Vishalakshi Temple &amp; Kaal Bhairav Temple</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Ramnagar </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Fort of King&nbsp;of Varanasi</span></p><p><br></p><h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">5</strong><sup style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"><strong>th</strong></sup><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"> Day :- Varanasi&nbsp;Local - Varanasi Local Sightseeing.</strong></h2><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Sarnath</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Dhamek Stupa, </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Chaukhandi Stupa </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Jain Temple</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Buddha temple</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Sarnath Museum,</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Ashok Pillar </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">Deer Park</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">In the evening visit Silk Weaving area of Varanasi for Shopping of Varanasi Products</span></p><p><br></p><h2><strong>6th Day : Transfer to Chitrakoot</strong></h2><p>Chitrakoot</p><p>Ramghat</p><p>Kamadgiri hill</p><p>Ram ghat</p><p>Hanuman Dhara, Kamadgiri, Bharat koop, Bharat milap Temple, Gupt Godavari, Janki kund, Sati Anusuya ashram, Sphatik shila, Ganesh Bagh, Valmiki ashram, Lakshman chowki, Ram Shaiyya&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h2><strong>7th Day : Transfer to Prayagraj</strong></h2><p>Allahabad Fort, Hanuman Temple, Anand Bhawan, Alopi Devi Temple, Veni Madhav Temple,</p><p><br></p><h2><strong>8th Day&nbsp;: Praygaraj to Sightseeng&nbsp;</strong></h2><p>Triveni Sangam the confluences of three River Ganga, Yamuna &amp; invisible Saraswati</p><p><br></p><h2><strong>9</strong><sup><strong>th</strong></sup><strong> Day : Prayagraj&nbsp;</strong></h2><p>Departure from prayagraj</p>', '<h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">5 % GST (03&nbsp;DBL Sharing Room)</strong></h2>', '<h1><strong>1st Day : Ayodhya Arrival &amp; Local Sightseeing </strong></h1><h2 class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">Arrival at ayodhya airport transfer to hotel &amp; Check in Hotel In Ayodhya, visit the historic Ram Janmabhoomi, believed to be the birthplace of Lord Rama, and explore the ancient Hanuman Garhi temple, immersing in the rich religious and cultural heritage of this sacred city in Uttar Pradesh, India.Evening Visit Sariyu River Aarti Overnight stay at Ayodhya.</span></h2><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><h1><strong>2nd Day : Ayodhya Local Sightseeing</strong></h1><h2>After Breakfast Visit the Kanak Bhavan, a sacred site associated with Lord Rama and his consort Sita. Dashrath bhavan, Sita Mata Rasoi, Guptar Ghat, Treata ke Thakur Second Half visit - Chappiya -Birth Place of SwamiNarayan Bhagwan. Overnight stay at Ayodhya.</h2><p>&nbsp;</p><h1><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">3</strong><sup style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"><strong>rd</strong></sup><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"> Day :-&nbsp;Ayodhya to Varanasi Sightseeing </strong></h1><h2>Arrival at Varanasi and transfer to the hotel,On arrival check in the hotel,Later visit .&nbsp;In the evening&nbsp;Ganga Aarti with Boat ride&nbsp;at Main Ghat,Dinner &amp; Overnight stay at&nbsp;Varanasi&nbsp;</h2><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><h1><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">4</strong><sup style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"><strong>th</strong></sup><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"> Day - Varanasi&nbsp;Local Sightseeing.</strong></h1><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">After Breakfast proceed to Gangaji for a holy dip and&nbsp;visit&nbsp;Main Kashi Vishwanath Temple, Annapurna Temple, Vishalakshi Temple &amp; Kaal Bhairav Temple, After lunch visit Ramnagar Fort of King&nbsp;of Varanasi, Overnight Stay at Varanasi.&nbsp;</span></h2><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">&nbsp;</span></p><h1><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">5</strong><sup style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"><strong>th</strong></sup><strong style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\"> Day :- Varanasi&nbsp;Local - Varanasi Local Sightseeing.</strong></h1><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23);\">After Breakfast Sarnath Tour -&nbsp;Sarnath is place where Lord Buddha preached first sermon after enlightenment, visit Dhamek Stupa, Chaukhandi Stupa, Jain Temple, Buddha temple, Sarnath Museum, Ashok Pillar, Deer Park, In the evening visit Silk Weaving area of Varanasi for Shopping of Varanasi Products, Overnight stay at Varanasi.</span></h2><h2>&nbsp;</h2><h1><strong>6th Day : Transfer to Chitrakoot</strong></h1><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h2>After Breakfast&nbsp;Visit Chitrakoot, a sacred town, to explore the Ramghat where Lord Rama is said to have bathed and performed rituals. Explore the Kamadgiri hill and other historic sites associated with Hindu mythology.&nbsp;Later visit Ram ghat, Hanuman Dhara, Kamadgiri, Bharat koop, Bharat milap Temple, Gupt Godavari, Janki kund, Sati Anusuya ashram, Sphatik shila, Ganesh Bagh, Valmiki ashram, Lakshman chowki, Ram Shaiyya&nbsp;Overnight stay at Chitrakoot</h2><p>&nbsp;</p><h1><strong>7th Day : Transfer to Prayagraj</strong></h1><h2>After Breakfast Check-out from hotel &amp; transfer to Prayagraj, On Arrival check in Hotel, Visit Allahabad Fort, Hanuman Temple, Anand Bhawan, Alopi Devi Temple, Veni Madhav Temple, Overnight stay at Prayagraj</h2><p><br></p><h1><strong>8th Day&nbsp;: Praygaraj to Sightseeng </strong></h1><h2>After Breakfast Chek-out from hotel &amp; visit Triveni Sangam the confluences of three River Ganga, Yamuna &amp; invisible Saraswati, Overnight stay at Prayagraj</h2><p>&nbsp;</p><h1><strong>9</strong><sup><strong>th</strong></sup><strong> Day : Prayagraj </strong></h1><h2 class=\"ql-align-justify\">After Breakfast transfer to prayagraj aiport&nbsp;and on time departure Pryagraj airport for connecting Flight to next destination with sweet memories.</h2><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p>', '<p><br></p>', '{}', 'Continental Plan (CP)', '2025-09-09 07:35:30', '2025-09-15 09:10:59', '5fdf3f54-18ef-4bf0-a329-1c826d07d84d', '0d88fbdc-1552-4281-a5de-206a35a3f42d', '09092025011_Q01', NULL, '{\"1757576420767\":{\"adults\":\"37000\",\"extraAdults\":\"\",\"childWithBed\":\"\",\"childWithoutBed\":\"\",\"childsBelow5\":\"\",\"remarks\":\"37000 Per person staying\\n12,500 Extra bed \\n\\n5 % GST (03 DBL Sharing Room)\",\"rows\":[{\"key\":\"1757576425537\",\"hotelName\":\"Hotel Click Narayana\",\"destination\":\"AYODHYA\",\"checkIn\":\"2025-11-01\",\"checkOut\":\"2025-09-03\",\"roomCategory\":\"Standard Room\",\"noOfRooms\":\"3\"},{\"key\":\"1757576488321\",\"hotelName\":\" Hotel Vishwam Residency\",\"destination\":\"VARANASI(BANARAS)\",\"checkIn\":\"2025-11-03\",\"checkOut\":\"2025-11-06\",\"roomCategory\":\"Standard Room\",\"noOfRooms\":\"3\"},{\"key\":\"1757576489415\",\"hotelName\":\"Hotel Parth\",\"destination\":\"CHITRAKOOT\",\"checkIn\":\"2025-11-06\",\"checkOut\":\"2025-11-08\",\"roomCategory\":\"Standard Room\",\"noOfRooms\":\"3\"},{\"key\":\"1757576497993\",\"hotelName\":\"Hotel Sukhdham\",\"destination\":\"PRRAYAGRAJ\",\"checkIn\":\"2025-11-08\",\"checkOut\":\"2025-11-09\",\"roomCategory\":\"Standard Room\",\"noOfRooms\":\"3\"}]}}'),
