('51f76948-292f-4167-94fd-f4ad52750db3', '27122025033', 'draft', '<ul><li>Accommodation in the mentioned in the hotel section.</li><li>Meal Plan As Mentioned In The Hotel Section.</li><li>Transfers and sightseeing by chosen vehicle As Per Given Itinerary.</li><li>Driver\'s bata, toll, parking, driver\'s night halt, fuel charges. (Applies if the vehicle is included in the package)</li><li>All transfers and sightseeing by AC Transport as per the itinerary inclusive of toll, parking &amp; driver’s batta ( from garage to garage 8 am – 8 pm)</li><li>All presently Applicable Govt Taxes. ( until mentioned as it is exclusive )</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Any Airfare / Train Fare Entrances fees / Monument Chargers /Tips and porter charges.</li><li>Expenses of personal nature such as drinks, telephone, Ayurveda massage and laundry bills etc.</li><li>Any boating charges (motor boat / pedal boat).</li><li>Any additional expenses incurred due to any flight delay or cancellation, weather conditions, political closures, technical faults etc</li><li>Early Check-in / Late Check-out</li><li>Any additional expenses incurred due to any flight delay or cancellation, weather conditions, political closures, technical faults, natural calamities etc.</li><li><strong style=\"color: rgb(133, 77, 14);\">NOTE: Anything not mentioned in the inclusions is excluded.</strong></li></ul>', '<p>1st Day&nbsp;(Fri, 6 Mar) : Bengaluru to Coorg - Arrival and Transfer</p><p>2nd Day&nbsp;(Sat, 7 Mar) : Coorg - Full Day Sightseeing</p><p>3rd Day&nbsp;(Sun, 8 Mar) : Coorg - Full Day Sightseeing</p><p>4th Day&nbsp;(Mon, 9 Mar) : Coorg to Ooty - Transfer and Ooty Sightseeing</p><p>5th Day&nbsp;(Tue, 10 Mar) : Ooty - Full Day Sightseeing</p><p>6th Day&nbsp;(Wed, 11 Mar) : Ooty - Full Day Sightseeing</p><p>7th Day&nbsp;(Thu, 12 Mar) : Ooty to Coimbatore - Transfer and Coimbatore Sightseeing</p>', '<p><br></p>', '{}', 'Modified American Plan (MAP)', '2025-12-27 12:20:15', '2025-12-29 06:34:53', NULL, '0cae09bb-571c-4816-