INSERT INTO `quotations` (`id`, `enquiryNo`, `status`, `inclusions`, `exclusions`, `itinerary`, `visaExclusions`, `flightDetails`, `mealPlan`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `leadId`, `userId`, `quotationNo`, `internalRemark`, `accommodationDetails`) VALUES
('ad1b3606-5263-4a05-857b-c9473a94adeb', '28102025026', 'draft', '<ul><li>﻿Welcome drink on arrival(No Alcoholic).&nbsp;</li><li>Accommodation On Twin Sharing Basis..&nbsp;</li><li>Meals as per chosen plan. (Served in hotel restaurant only)&nbsp;</li><li>All Transfers&amp; Local Sightseeing on Pvt basis Included as per itinerary if included.&nbsp;</li><li>All Toll, Tax, Permit, Parking, D.A Included if transport service selected.&nbsp;</li><li>Rates Given on Twin Sharing Basis.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Mandatory X-mas and New Year Eve Gala Dinner charges will be Extra as per Hotel Policy.&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>', '<ul><li>Any sightseeing or entry to park/Monument/museum/anything not includes in the inclusions list</li><li>Tips, Telephone Charges,Laundry.</li><li>Any Guide charges.</li><li>The Package is valid for travels dates only.</li><li>AC &amp; Music System in Vehicle will not be operated when we are on the hilly areas.&nbsp;</li></ul>', '<ul><li><strong>Day 1 : 05 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong> Chandigarh Arrival and Transfer To Manali Hotel (Approx. 270Kms/08-09 Hrs)</strong></p><p><strong> Hello Manali!</strong></p><ul><li>Arrive at Chandigarh Airport/Railway Station and drive to Manali, enjoying scenic stops such as Sundernagar Valley, Mandi, Pandoh Dam, Hanogi Devi Temple, Beas River Viewpoint, Aut Tunnel, Kullu, and the Shawl Factory. Upon arrival, check in to your hotel. Spend the evening at leisure, Have a lip-smacking dinner and stay overnight at Manali.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Day 2 : 06 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Manali Local Sightseeing</strong></p><p><strong>Hello Manali!</strong></p><ul><li>Explore Manali’s top attractions, including Tibetan Monastery, Van Vihar, Mall Road and Club house. Visit Hadimba Devi Temple and Manu Temple for blessings. Spend the evening at leisure. Have a lip-smacking dinner and stay overnight at Manali.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Day 3 : 07 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Manali Local sightseeing - Naggar Castle Full Day</strong></p><p><strong>Hello Manali!</strong></p><ul><li>After breakfast, visit Naggar Castle – explore the architecture, museum &amp; wooden temples inside,Visit Nicholas Roerich Art Gallery &amp; Estate,Walk to Tripura Sundari Temple,Stroll Naggar village for local crafts.Return to Manali, Have a lip-smacking dinner and stay overnight at Manali.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong> Day 04 : 08 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Manali Local- Solang Valley Including Or Rohtang Pass (At Own Cost)</strong></p><p><strong>Hello Manali!</strong></p><ul><li>A trip to Manali isn’t complete without visiting Solang Valley, known for adventure activities like paragliding, skiing, Cable Car Ride and ATV rides. Stop by the Beas River for serene views and photography, while returning en-route visit Vashisth Temple. Alternatively, head to Rohtang Pass (3,979 m) for snow activities and breathtaking vistas. Return to Manali, Have a lip-smacking dinner and stay overnight at Manali.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Day 05 : 09 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Manali Hotel To Dharamshala Hotel Transfer (Approx. 240Kms/08-09 Hrs)</strong></p><p><strong>Goodbye Manali, Hello Dharamshala!</strong></p><ul><li>After breakfast check out from hotel then drive to Dharamshala. Enjoy Scenic views enroute towards Dharamshala will just make your day. Cherish a summer retreat as you at your hotel in Dharamshala. Have a lip-smacking dinner and stay overnight at Dharamshala.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Day 06 : 10 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Dharamshala Hotel To Dalhousie Hotel Transfer (Approx. 130Kms/03-04 Hrs)</strong></p><p><strong>Goodbye Dharamshala, Hello Dalhousie!</strong></p><ul><li>After breakfast, explore Mcleodganj and Dharamsala’s key attractions including the Dalai Lama Temple (Tsuglagkhang), Bhagsu Nag Temple, St. John’s Church, Naddi View Point, Dal Lake, Cricket Stadium and Norbulingka Institute. Enjoy the Tibetan market and drive to Dalhousie. Situated at 2039 mts in the outer slope s of the Dhaula Dhar range with its natural beauty and natural surroundings. On arrival check- in at the hotel. Have a lip-smacking dinner and stay overnight at Dalhousie.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Day 07 : 11 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Dalhousie Local Sightseeing- Khajjiar Day Trip (Approx. 23Kms/01 Hrs)</strong></p><p><strong>Hello Dalhousie!</strong></p><ul><li>Today morning after breakfast drive to Khajjiar, 23 kms from Dalhousie by road is the mini Switzerland of India i.e. Khajjiar, at a height of 6400 ft. Hutchison writes, \"Khajjiar is a forest glade of great beauty, 6400 feet above sea level\" known as the mini Switzerland of India and is surrounded by dense pine and deodar forests. There is a small lake in the center with a floating island and 9-hole golf course here. Enjoy zorbing &amp; paragliding (on direct payment basis). Visit Khajjiar Sanctuary &amp; Khajinag Temple at Khajjiar, known as one of the most charming spots in the Himalayas, have a lip-smacking dinner and stay overnight at Dalhousie.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Day 08 : 12 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Dalhousie Hotel To Amritsar Hotel Transfer (Approx. 200 Kms/05-06 Hrs)</strong></p><p><strong>Goodbye Dalhousie, Hello Amritsar!</strong></p><ul><li>After Breakfast, check out and drive to Amritsar. On arrival, check in to the hotel.&nbsp;Experience the patriotic ceremony, holiest shrine. visit Golden Temple-also called as Harmandir Sahib and Jallianwala Bagh. Evening visit to Wagah Border and get to see the flag-lowering ceremony on India-Pakistan border. In the evening return back to the hotel, have a lip-smacking dinner and stay overnight at Amritsar.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Day 09 : 13 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Amritsar Local Sightseeing</strong></p><p><strong>Hello Amritsar!</strong></p><ul><li>After a healthy breakfast, you will visit to different tourist attraction places in Amritsar. The list includes Ram Bagh, Saada Pind, Gobindgarh Fort, Statue of Maharaja RanjitSinh and Explore Local Market and do shopping. The main allurement of Ram Bagh is the summer palace museum of Maharaja Ranjit Singh which also has a history of its own. You will then return to the hotel, have a lip-smacking dinner and stay overnight at Amritsar.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Day 10 : 14 Feb</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Amritsar Hotel To Amritsar Railway Station/Airport Drop</strong></p><p><strong>Goodbye Amritsar!</strong></p><ul><li>The next morning you will check out after breakfast. After checkout, a drive will take, you to Airport/Railway station. This is how this amazing trip ends, and you will be dropped comfortable to the continue your onward journey back home.&nbsp;</li></ul>', '<p><br></p>', '{}', 'Continental Plan (CP)', '2025-10-28 11:21:39', '2025-10-29 11:13:55', '13dd48b3-7274-4bc6-b171-750abcf9120e', '0d88fbdc-1552-4281-a5de-206a35a3f42d', '28102025026_Q01', NULL, '{\"1761724290069\":{\"adults\":\"17900\",\"extraAdults\":\"\",\"childWithBed\":\"\",\"childWithoutBed\":\"\",\"childsBelow5\":\"\",\"remarks\":\"\",\"rows\":[{\"key\":\"1761724297179\",\"hotelName\":\"Surya Inn & Suites\",\"destination\":\"Manali\",\"checkIn\":\"2026-02-05\",\"checkOut\":\"2026-02-09\",\"roomCategory\":\"Premium\",\"noOfRooms\":\"3\"},{\"key\":\"1761724520667\",\"hotelName\":\"The Origin Dharamshala\",\"destination\":\"Dharamshala\",\"checkIn\":\"2026-02-09\",\"checkOut\":\"2026-02-10\",\"roomCategory\":\"Super Deluxe\",\"noOfRooms\":\"3\"},{\"key\":\"1761724578023\",\"hotelName\":\"The Mohan Palace Dalhousie\",\"destination\":\"Dalhousie\",\"checkIn\":\"2026-02-10\",\"checkOut\":\"2026-02-12\",\"roomCategory\":\"Standard\",\"noOfRooms\":\"3\"},{\"key\":\"1761724638815\",\"hotelName\":\"Dewdrop Shankh Hotel , Amritsar\",\"destination\":\"Amritsar\",\"checkIn\":\"2026-02-12\",\"checkOut\":\"2026-02-14\",\"roomCategory\":\"Deluxe\",\"noOfRooms\":\"3\"}]}}'),
